flowchart TD
    Run["Text2SQL Run"] --> Replay["Replay Evidence"]
    Replay --> Classify["Classify failure layer"]
    Classify --> Eval["Promote to eval case"]
    Eval --> Regression["Regression suite"]
    Regression --> Patch["Improve schema / metric / retrieval / prompt / validator"]
    Patch --> NextRun["Next Text2SQL Run"]
    NextRun --> Replay

    Replay --> Metrics["Accuracy and safety metrics"]
    Metrics --> Prioritize["Prioritize weakest plane"]
    Prioritize --> Patch
